channel.title: WWE's Greatest Moments
channel.desc: Otherwise known as Cactus Jack, Mankind and Dude Love, Mick Foley is one of the most beloved Superstars of all-time. For over four decades, Foley has entertained audiences worldwide as The Hardcore Legend. We look back at some of the greatest times in Mick Foley's career with such moments as the unforgettable Hell in a Cell match against the Undertaker, Cactus Jack's debut at Madison Square Garden, Foley achieving his lifelong dream of becoming WWE Champion, and more!
